# Elegant Editorial Typography-Focused - Website Design System

## Website Metadata
- **Source URL:** https://www.vogue.co.uk/
- **Design Style:** Elegant Editorial Typography-Focused
- **Primary Framework:** Angular
- **CSS Framework:** Material UI / Styled Components
- **Analysis Date:** 2025-11-29
