## Design Overview

British Vogue's website embodies an elegant, editorial design system that prioritizes typography and content hierarchy. The design is characterized by a sophisticated black-and-white color palette with minimal color accents, allowing the editorial content and typography to take center stage. The layout follows magazine-style principles with clean spacing, serif fonts for body content, and sans-serif fonts for UI elements. The design system emphasizes readability, visual hierarchy, and a premium editorial aesthetic.

